Yeah no problem! Let's see, when I tried sublingual it was my first time messing with Hbwr and I heard about how bad the stomach cramps/nasusa was suppose to be so I tried my hardest not to swallow anything at all.
The second time I tried it I decided to just flat out chew and swallow 3 seeds. The nasusa/stomach discomfort came way before any of the effects (took 2 hours to get visuals) and it was pretty annoying at just 3 seeds. I didn't need to puke persay, but it didn't feel good at all and subtracted from the experience.
Now the third time I did it, I look online and saw that people use that over the counter nasusa medicine (dramamine) 30ish mins before taking the seeds to reduce the nasusa. So I tried it and it definitely works. I still felt a little discomfort but it wasnt distracting from the experience at all.
So I recommend taking some with some dramamine to help with the nausea.
